{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","title":"requestProgress","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/requestProgress":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"title":"requestProgress","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","title":"MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown","title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification"}}}